divs: Sighting Details1. Where were you and what were you doing at the time? This was after dinner i went outside to relax and look at the sky. 2. What made you first notice the object? I seen a black object, like a circle fly slowly. 3. What did you think the object was when you first noticed it? I had no idea, tas very small, so i didn't think plane. Probably wasn't, unless a private jet which is black or brown, or a weather balloon. 4. Describe the object and its actions and motions. It was flying slowly East for 3 minutes, then turned North. 5. Describe your feelings, reactions and actions, during and after sighting the object. I was elated. Not my first sighting, sure as hell wasn't no plane i ever seen. 6. How did you lose sight of the object? It turned North and either dissapeared into the clouds or vanished. I honestly couldn't make out what the object was, but it had a general shape of a circle.
